data.name: label35.Text
data.value: • To make an order, just click on the dish you would like to taste • If you want to remove a dish from the order - select it and use the red-cross button. A click without selecting will clear all you order • Can not wait to find out the components of dish - choose it and click the yellow-question button • Do not forget about portion and amount - manage them using central controls • To confirm the order - push "Confirm" button and to pay for it - a button lower
